Pacnet is no better than cyberway. In terms of packet loss..they may have less problems sometimes.
But in terms of lag..they are the champions. Singnet and Cyberway win out in lag over Pacnet any day.
Trust me i know i used both Cyberway and Pacnet unlimited a/cs before.

Good isp hunting!

Zanderion
